turn-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104daw1665702633024.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/daw1665702633024.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/daw1665702633024.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"daw1665702633024\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101621e1_d101622e1_d101623e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n         \n                                ImgSelect\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">@<var class=\"keyword varname\">ImageFile</var>\n</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">^<var class=\"keyword varname\">GlyphName</var>\n</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"daw1665702633024__section_drq_ls2_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268674e77\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"daw1665702633024__table_d11957e1_d11958e1_d11959e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">For widgets, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Default Image</span> must\n                be set.<p class=\"p\">For command buttons, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> must be set to\n                    <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"daw1665702633024__section_gnm_st2_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268674e134\">Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101630e1_d101631e1_d101632e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For more\n        information, see the \"$properties and \"$fieldproperties\" topics.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"daw1665702633024__pre_mzf_grl_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"ImgDefault=@filesave.png<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>ImgSelect=@filesave_sel.png\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"daw1665702633024__section_ngm_grl_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268674e155\">Setting for Menus</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101636e1_d101637e1_d101638e1\">For menus, this property can only be set in the\n        application initialization file and applies to all menus. If  ImgSelect is set, it overrides the  BackColorSelect property.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101639e1_d101640e1_d101641e1\">In <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"daw1665702633024__pre_u2d_3rl_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[application]\nmenu=umenu(ForeColor=black;ImgSelect=@yellow.png)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"daw1665702633024__section_z5j_3rl_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d268674e177\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"daw1665702633024__ul_dhl_jrl_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"daw1665702633024__li_d41201e1_d41202e1_d41203e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101645e1_d101646e1_d101647e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"daw1665702633024__li_d41204e1_d41205e1_d41206e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101648e1_d101649e1_d101650e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"daw1665702633024__li_d41207e1_d41208e1_d41209e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"daw1665702633024__p_d101651e1_d101652e1_d101653e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfw1705577424699.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfw1705577424699.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.\">Menu Objects</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dte1665702632952.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Default Image (ImgDefault)</a><p>The image that is displayed as the button or tab.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$properties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldproperties</a><p>Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612512\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Active Image (ImgSelect) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The image that is displayed when the button, tab, or menu item is selected. \" ImgSelect = @ ImageFile | ^ GlyphName \" Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: For widgets, Default Image must be set. For command buttons, Representation must be set to Uniface . Setting in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see the \"$properties and \"$fieldproperties\" topics. $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"ImgDefault=@filesave.png ; ImgSelect=@filesave_sel.png\" Copy Setting for Menus For menus, this property can only be set in the application initialization file and applies to all menus. If ImgSelect is set, it overrides the BackColorSelect property. In usys.ini : [application] menu=umenu(ForeColor=black;ImgSelect=@yellow.png) Copy Applies To CommandButton utabex (TabEx) Menu Objects Related Links Default Image (ImgDefault) The image that is displayed as the button or tab. Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. $properties Return or set the current widget properties of a field. $fieldproperties Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}